            "body": "I'm in favor of renaming a lot of these, but `bufnr` is also prevalent so we're kind of stuck. But it's probably at least feasible to get rid of `buffer` everywhere (soft-deprecate), and accept that `buf` and `bufnr` are just going to be around forever.",
